title: 180: 2017 First Round Draft Buzz
itunes:title: 180: 2017 First Round Draft Buzz
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks reveal all of the latest buzz surrounding the first round heading into the 2017 NFL Draft from Philadelphia. The guys also give their favorite 2nd and 3rd day prospects as well as their pick for the next Dak Prescott in this draft class.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
